{"tid":1818959,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"涉暴動案保釋期間涉嫌再犯事 中三生涉縱火罪還押候審","createTime":"2020-01-10T10:58:37.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-11T00:23:41.000Z","uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"7d12364fa1586e572ad98be312ff544377201a74","tid":1818959,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-10T10:58:37.000Z","msg":"一名中三學生涉嫌本月8日凌晨在元朗朗晴居對開向馬路投擲汽油彈，被控一項縱火罪，涉案學生押解到屯門裁判法院應訊，由於他涉及另一宗暴動案件，涉嫌保釋期間再度犯事，裁判官拒絕他的保釋申請，案件押後至4月初處理。事發時有警車途經，警員聽到聲響，將他拘捕，警車的行車攝錄儀拍攝到他掟汽油彈的過程，亦有閉路電視拍攝到被告離家上街的情況，警方在現場檢獲兩樽各3公升的汽油，需要時間等候指模校對結果，裁判官應控方申請將案件押後至4月3日，等候鑑證報告及索取法律意見。<br />\n<br />\n2020-01-10 18:41:58"},{"pid":"b49c0d4bd4a4a9567e426c8c88feca997199f426","tid":1818959,"uid":52090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-10T11:02:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ec512ed7615e635cf7664ff7153fa416bffd8a4","tid":1818959,"uid":8014,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-10T11:03:03.000Z","msg":"凌晨在元朗朗晴居對開向馬路投擲汽油彈<br />\n<br />\nwhy?"},{"pid":"07b1987def762947bb20fcba65092b5fbd398218","tid":1818959,"uid":235152,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2ec512ed7615e635cf7664ff7153fa416bffd8a4","tid":1818959,"uid":8014,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-10T11:03:03.000Z","msg":"凌晨在元朗朗晴居對開向馬路投擲汽油彈<br />\n<br />\nwhy?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-10T11:14:40.000Z","msg":"應該係諗住去某地方擲<br />\n但感覺俾人跟蹤咪掉曬落馬路走人<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a93a45b95d4baca78fdf4c3952ffae03e6ab575","tid":1818959,"uid":253253,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-10T17:49:33.000Z","msg":"冇人回, 變左condom"},{"pid":"d876b72186631179daba838605ef4fde7f90c858","tid":1818959,"uid":59976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-1